---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "About LSY Blog",
	title: "About",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<h1 class="title mb-6">About</h1>
	<div class="about-copy prose prose-sm prose-cactus max-w-none">
		<p>
			My name is Sung-Young (성영) Lee (이). "Sung" (晟) means bright, and "Young" (榮) means glory.
			"Lee" (李) is my family name.
		</p>
		<h2>Past</h2>
			<div class="military-entry not-prose my-4 flex items-center gap-3">
					<img
						alt="USAG Humphreys"
						class="bg-global-bg h-14 w-14 shrink-0 rounded-md object-contain p-1"
						height="56"
						src="/usarmy.jpg"
						width="56"
					/>
				<div>
					<p class="mb-0">
						<strong class="text-accent"
							>Military Service at the United States Army Garrison (USAG) Humphreys.</strong
						>
					</p>
					<p class="mb-0">Sergeant, 18 months service, 557th Military Police Company.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		<div class="military-entry not-prose my-4 flex items-center gap-3">
			<div class="bg-global-bg h-14 w-14 shrink-0 rounded-md p-1">
				<img
					alt="Seoul National University"
					class="h-full w-full object-contain"
					height="56"
					src="/snu.jpg"
					width="56"
				/>
			</div>
			<div>
				<p class="mb-0">
					<strong class="text-accent">B.S. in EECS (Summa Cum Laude) from Seoul National University (Advisor: Prof. Deog-Kyoon Jeong).</strong>
				</p>
				<p class="mb-0">
					Samsung 28nm, TSMC 40nm Tape-out Experience on Wireline Interface Circuits.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="military-entry not-prose my-4 flex items-center gap-3">
			<div class="bg-global-bg h-14 w-14 shrink-0 rounded-md p-1">
				<img
					alt="The University of Texas at Austin"
					class="h-full w-full object-contain"
					height="56"
					src="/utaustin.jpg"
					width="56"
				/>
			</div>
			<div>
				<p class="mb-0">
					<strong class="text-accent">Ph.D. student at UT Austin (Advisor: Prof. David Z. Pan).</strong>
				</p>
				<p class="mb-0">Research on transistor-level Electronics Design Automation (EDA).</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<h2>Current</h2>
		<div class="military-entry not-prose my-4 flex items-center gap-3">
			<div class="bg-global-bg h-14 w-14 shrink-0 rounded-md p-1">
				<img
					alt="The University of Texas at Austin"
					class="h-full w-full object-contain"
					height="56"
					src="/utaustin.jpg"
					width="56"
				/>
			</div>
			<div>
				<p class="mb-0">
					<strong class="text-accent">Ph.D. student at UT Austin (Advisor: Prof. Keshav K. Pingali).</strong>
				</p>
				<p class="mb-0">Research on Reinforcement Learning and ML Systems.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<h2 id="original-intro">Research Focus</h2>
		<p><strong class="text-accent">Maximize both Expressivity & Efficiency in Robotics.</strong></p>
		<p>Specific short term interests are as follows:</p>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li>
				Algorithms
				<br />
				(1) Diffusion Models / Flow Matching (for expressive behavior cloning)
				<br />
				(2) Reinforcement Learning (for efficient real-time learning)
			</li>
			<li>
				Systems
				<br />
				(1) GPU Programming (for efficient RL training and inference)
				<br />
				(2) Distributed systems (for efficient MARL systems)
			</li>
		</ul>
		<h2>Honors and Awards</h2>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li>
				DAC Young Fellowship, 62nd Design Automation Conference (DAC)
				(Jun. 2025)
			</li>
			<li>
				UT Excellence Engineering Fellowship, UT Austin
				(Sep. 2024)
			</li>
			<li>
				Golden Tiger Award, USAG Humphreys
				(Dec. 2019)
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</PageLayout>

<style>
	.about-copy p + p {
		margin-top: -1rem;
	}

	.military-entry p + p {
		margin-top: 0.1rem;
	}
</style>
